    body: "Welcome to the journey. What you're about to experience is not a program—it's an invitation to remember what you already know. The Connection Room was built because I believe that the deepest part of human experience happens in moments of genuine connection, vulnerable honesty, and embodied presence. Over the next weeks, you'll be met with reflections, practices, and conversations designed to wake you up to what's already alive in you. Trust the process. Trust yourself.",
